Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚮往天空 親近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.14,0:00:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翱翔於天空的神秘力量開始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏有一個傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在天之邊際雲之彼方存在著一片黃金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個故事講述了一個追尋夢想自由生存的天空盜賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.51,0:00:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空盜團少年——酷的波瀾起伏的愛和冒險的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.96,0:02:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ChaosChoir的刺客擬煌珠菲蘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.83,0:02:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她愛上了酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喜歡上了蕾 希絲卡他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.24,0:02:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後為了保護酷捨棄生命結束了短暫虛幻的一生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.57,0:02:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對於菲蘿來說的幸福到底是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.89,0:02:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抑制住心痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.62,0:02:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷他們再次啟程前往煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.24,0:02:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十一唱 道破的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.37,0:02:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們朝煌珠樂園出發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.30,0:03:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也為了讓像菲蘿的悲劇不再重演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.19,0:03:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個叫菲蘿的女孩我一開始就沒對她抱什麼希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.55,0:03:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼 古拉迪亞斯也出乎意料沒什麼用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.10,0:03:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只需再忍耐一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.84,0:04:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.20,0:04:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.35,0:04:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.40,0:04:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.65,0:04:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.15,0:04:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.70,0:04:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.22,0:04:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.60,0:04:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊芙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.32,0:04:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像又聽見那個叫伊芙的人的聲音了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.60,0:04:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是像這樣痛苦還是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.59,0:04:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺樣子有點不對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.55,0:04:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.42,0:04:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快點找個地方讓蕾休息的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.91,0:04:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從這再往南走一點路好像就有村子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.64,0:04:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是菲蘿打算回去的那個村子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.45,0:05:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎樣先去那個村子看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.81,0:05:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正也得找今晚過夜的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.79,0:05:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以的話想讓蕾睡在好一點的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.57,0:05:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得快點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.90,0:05:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留給我們的時間不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.82,0:05:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上天之皇女{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.62,0:05:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自土中誕生{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.34,0:05:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩惠缺水之況{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.35,0:05:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齋宮枝繁葉茂{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.31,0:05:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,綠意蔥蔥{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.59,0:05:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不斷噬嚙{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.52,0:05:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顯露真相{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.86,0:05:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分賜靈力{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.93,0:05:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,降生之女{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.00,0:05:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽命順從{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是這裏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.30,0:06:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.38,0:06:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除此之外找不到其它通往村子的路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.37,0:06:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏就是菲蘿小時候居住的村子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.05,0:06:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像已經沒人居住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.55,0:06:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣子實在讓人無法安心休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.70,0:06:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.83,0:07:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏易於放哨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.84,0:07:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到煌珠樂園居然已發展到那種地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.19,0:07:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經下令休納貝爾的偵察隊出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.05,0:07:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裝備一旦到位 守護翼全軍就出動攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.15,0:07:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道沒有什麼能避免全面衝突的對策嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.11,0:07:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總監
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.32,0:07:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.64,0:07:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.34,0:07:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希絲卡他們現在應該正同七煌寶樹一起前往那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.41,0:07:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣的話 他們就會有被捲入戰鬥的危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.15,0:07:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉打攪一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.05,0:07:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點事情想跟您說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙威魯德啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.59,0:07:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.30,0:08:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你調到休納貝爾手下後的積極表現廣為流傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.25,0:08:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.01,0:08:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是把兩位在學院所教給我的付諸於實踐而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.13,0:08:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 你想說的是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.04,0:08:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你即將隨休納貝爾的偵察隊前往煌珠樂園吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.66,0:08:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.65,0:08:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是為此而來找您談的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.08,0:08:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.20,0:08:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前幾天執行任務負傷住院期間希絲卡他們來看望過我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.47,0:08:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為此事特地過來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.86,0:08:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.74,0:08:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然不能給你添麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.70,0:08:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但希絲卡他們的事還請多多照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.42,0:08:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 我會盡力而為的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.10,0:08:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 我先告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.47,0:09:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然知道ChaosChoir不會就此罷休
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.38,0:09:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但手上的武器只剩下一匣煙霧彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.80,0:09:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,形式嚴峻啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.91,0:09:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.64,0:09:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.62,0:09:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好擔心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.31,0:09:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又聽見伊芙的聲音了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.97,0:10:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在悲切地呼喚我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.04,0:10:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「救救我」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.48,0:10:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「快來」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.52,0:10:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在要好好休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.67,0:10:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好起來後早點去煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.25,0:10:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.94,0:10:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.61,0:11:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ChaosChoir的擬煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.92,0:11:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.66,0:11:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是ChaosChoir的基盧特魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.66,0:11:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請把七煌寶樹蕾芙麗·梅札蘭斯大人交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.33,0:11:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.88,0:11:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼就只有強奪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.57,0:11:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,烈火炎炎{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.75,0:11:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靈魂狂怒似蛇{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此刻 覺醒吧{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.16,0:11:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個敵人我們來對付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.55,0:11:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩你帶著酷和蕾快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.69,0:11:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.00,0:11:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上了 奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.09,0:11:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.25,0:11:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走了 酷 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.14,0:12:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.39,0:12:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是守護翼的希絲卡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.47,0:12:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早就想見你一面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.24,0:12:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你又是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.62,0:12:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是ChaosChoir的阿京娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.57,0:12:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別因為我可愛就小看我哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.11,0:12:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是很有兩下子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.13,0:12:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.99,0:12:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人由我來對付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.15,0:12:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷你帶著蕾快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.68,0:12:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.50,0:12:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.74,0:12:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這麼點能量嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.16,0:12:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿京娜我失望透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.28,0:12:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 這也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.48,0:13:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擬煌珠不過是碎石而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.15,0:13:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽我之命{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.76,0:13:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幻作肢體{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.02,0:13:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與我融合{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.86,0:13:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.38,0:13:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,碎石的替代品要多少有多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.43,0:13:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是你的戰鬥方式嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.39,0:13:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很久沒遇到高手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.46,0:13:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是...
